ing: 1 (10.75 ounce) can  condensed chicken gumbo soup
des: "Very simple. I grew up in Iowa and I always thought these originated there. Serve on warm seeded buns."
ins: In large skillet over medium heat, cook ground beef until brown, 5 to 10 minutes.  Drain.  Return meat to skillet, with soup.  Simmer until heated through, 5 minutes.  Serve hot.
